# Copy to .env and fill in. NEVER commit .env.
#
# Family access gate. Store only the SHA-256 hash of the access code, never the
# code itself. Generate the hash with:
#
#   node scripts/hash-code.mjs "your-family-code"
#
# Note: a client-side gate keeps the app out of casual/search-engine reach but is
# NOT real authentication (the bundle is downloadable). For stronger protection,
# put Cloudflare Access in front of the deployment — see docs/SECURITY.md.
VITE_ACCESS_CODE_HASH=
